dct_description_sm: Map of German South West Africa showing the westernmost portion of the Bechuanaland Protectorate and Bechuanaland, district boundaries according to the 1912 edition, railways according to the 1925 supplement, main roads, towns, rivers and other water sources, and mountains.
Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Bar scale on map given in "km."
Die Ortszeichen "o" bedeuten nicht immer bewohnte Orte, sondern öfters nur Wasserstellen oder sonstige Lokalitäten verschiedner Art.
